1.1.name: wordpress/figero
1.1.description: Figero is a great Theme to build your business or services related website with ease. The Theme comes with a very simple to use themes options panel through which you can configure literally anything on your website. The theme is very simplistic yet modern in design and really very easy to built your website upon.
